Remove experimental support for [MSC3932](https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-spec-proposals/pull/3932), [MSC3931](https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-spec-proposals/pull/3931), [MSC3381](https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-spec-proposals/pull/3381), [MSC4028](https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-spec-proposals/pull/4028), and [MSC3664](https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-spec-proposals/pull/3664).
